description:
Dass das Kliemannsland nicht nur zu Land eine Menge zu bieten hat, wissen wir sp√§testens seit der Auszeichnung als eine der 10 beliebtesten Wassersportanlagen Deutschlands. Damit uns der Erfolg nicht in den Tiefenrausch treibt, legen wir heute ne Schippe drauf.
Neben den laufenden Pl√§nen f√ºr einen 29 ¬Ω Meter Sprungturm, einen Aggro-Aqua-Aerobic Kurs mit Hannes Petersen und einer von Brian JakuBOMBski muskelbetriebenen Wellenmaschine, hat auch die DLRG Niedersachsen unser feuchtes Monopolpotenzial erkannt. Mit Joel‚Äôs Aggregatoren-Traum zahlloser N√§chte und einer fahrenden Bierbank aufm Bock haben sie uns besucht und ein Geschenk mitgebracht: einen Tauchturm. title: Inside the World's Most Luxurious Abandoned City (never seen before)
description:
Thanks to Audible for sponsoring this episode. Go to http://www.audible.com/yestheory or text "yestheory" to 500 500 and start listening today!

Check out my friend @Johnny Harris first story about this conflict here:
https://youtu.be/p7_TZagxjyk

Check out @Nathaniel Drew ‚Äòs Channel who joined us on this trip as well.

This was probably one of the most complicated stories we've ever had to tell. For my Cypriots watching, I wish you peace and prosperity for the future. I hope you enjoyed this piece and understand that not every single detail of the story could be highlighted. I could've spent hours going into all of the intricacies of this conflict and tried to stay balance and unbiased as I simply came an observer.

Varosha is one of the largest and most tragic ghost towns on the planet. Once filled with tens of thousands of tourists every year it's been abandoned now for about 47 years... The conflict in Cyprus is far from being resolved and unfortunately is growing in complexity as the years go by. Sending hope and positivity to all the Cypriots out there, thank you for hosting me in your country.

title: THE BATMAN ‚Äì Main Trailer
description:
It‚Äôs not just a call‚Ä¶ It‚Äôs a warning. 
 
From Warner Bros. Pictures comes Matt Reeves‚Äô ‚ÄúThe Batman,‚Äù starring Robert Pattinson in the dual role of Gotham City‚Äôs vigilante detective and his alter ego, reclusive billionaire Bruce Wayne. Starring alongside Pattinson (‚ÄúTenet,‚Äù ‚ÄúThe Lighthouse‚Äù) as Gotham‚Äôs famous and infamous cast of characters are Zo√´ Kravitz (‚ÄúBig Little Lies,‚Äù ‚ÄúFantastic Beasts: The Crimes of Grindelwald‚Äù) as Selina Kyle; Paul Dano (‚ÄúLove & Mercy,‚Äù ‚Äú12 Years a Slave‚Äù) as Edward Nashton; Jeffrey Wright (‚ÄúNo Time to Die,‚Äù ‚ÄúWestworld‚Äù) as the GCPD‚Äôs James Gordon; John Turturro (the ‚ÄúTransformers‚Äù films, ‚ÄúThe Plot Against America‚Äù) as Carmine Falcone; Peter Sarsgaard (‚ÄúThe Magnificent Seven,‚Äù ‚ÄúInterrogation‚Äù) as Gotham D.A. Gil Colson; Jayme Lawson (‚ÄúFarewell Amor‚Äù) as mayoral candidate Bella Re√°l; with Andy Serkis (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films, ‚ÄúBlack Panther‚Äù) as Alfred; and Colin Farrell (‚ÄúThe Gentlemen,‚Äù ‚ÄúFantastic Beasts and Where to Find Them‚Äù) as Oswald Cobblepot. Reeves (‚ÄúThe Planet of the Apes‚Äù franchise) directed from a screenplay by Reeves & Peter Craig, based on characters from DC.  Batman was created by Bob Kane with Bill Finger.  Dylan Clark (the ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù films) and Reeves produced the film, with Michael E. Uslan, Walter Hamada, Chantal Nong Vo and Simon Emanuel serving as executive producers.   The director‚Äôs behind-the-scenes creative team included Oscar-nominated director of photography Greig Fraser (‚ÄúDune,‚Äù ‚ÄúLion‚Äù); Reeves‚Äô ‚ÄúPlanet of the Apes‚Äù production designer, James Chinlund, and editor, William Hoy; editor Tyler Nelson (‚ÄúRememory‚Äù); and Oscar-winning costume designer Jacqueline Durran (‚Äú1917,‚Äù ‚ÄúLittle Women,‚Äù ‚ÄúAnna Karenina‚Äù).  The music is by Oscar-winning composer Michael Giacchino (the current ‚ÄúSpider-Man,‚Äù ‚ÄúJurassic World‚Äù and ‚ÄúStar Wars‚Äù films, ‚ÄúUp‚Äù). Warner Bros. Pictures Presents a 6th & Idaho/Dylan Clark Productions Production, a Matt Reeves Film, ‚ÄúThe Batman.‚Äù  The film is set to open in theaters March 4, 2022 and will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures.
